release.notes:
Embossed gold CBS Masterworks affixed to Top Right Hand Corner of sleeve
Some copies may have a Gold Stamped Promo over the barcode on rear of sleeve
G1 in runout indicates [l442751]

Digital recording.
The same release also appeared on cassette.

The liner notes on the sleeve are English; a page with translations in German and French is provided. The inner anti-static sleeve is printed with the CBS Masterworks logo.
